Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 211 Regent Ave W is located on Old Transcona's commercial high street in the heart of the downtown. There has been tremendous growth in the last five years in nearby communities. The building has been completely redeveloped and has strong visibility and prominent signage, as well as abundant onsite parking.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: North Town Centre is a modern take on the timeless village square. It’s a short walk from Bridgwater’s homes and condos, and it will feature lively places to gather, shop and dine. The architecture and amenities look to the future, with details like fibre cement shakes and underground waste management. Free-standing, pad, drive-thru, and strip opportunities available. We’re seeking businesses with the products, services and community mindedness that every great neighbourhood needs.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: National tenants include Safeway, CIBC, McDonalds, and Subway. Excellent access and egress from Portage Avenue andCavalier Drive. Approximately 73,800 vehicles per day pass through the light controlled intersection at Portage Avenue and Cavalier Drive.

Modern, clean and attractively finished unit available in improved form, or can be brought back to shell condition. Current layout includes large open reception area, private office, private boardroom, kitchen and washroom.

Option 1: Prime retail opportunity offering 1,400 SF traditional rectangular unit with 20’ of frontage for $26 net PSF. Ideal for traditional retail, office and medical uses. Bonus storage space at no extra charge. Option 2: Superb value for 3,296 square feet in a grocery-anchored retail centre for only $14.00 PSF. Attractive opportunity for all medical and office users looking for retail traffic, amenities and abundant free parking. Also available for many retail uses.
